#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kalarm.appdata.xml:43
msgid "Fix sound files being played at the wrong volume when using VLC."
msgstr ""
"Corrige files de sono que es reproducite al volumine errate quando  il es "
"usante VLC."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kalarm.appdata.xml:51
msgid ""
"Fix hang evaluating recurring date-only alarms when start-of-day time is non-"
"zero."
msgstr ""
"Corrige le bloco de evalutation del alarmas recurrente de solo data quando "
"le tempore de initio del die es non zero."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kalarm.appdata.xml:52
msgid ""
"Fix hang evaluating next recurrence time for time zones with daylight "
"savings time."
msgstr ""
"Corrige le bloco de evalutation del proxime tempore  de recurrentia per "
"zonas de tempore con hora estive."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kalarm.appdata.xml:60
msgid "Prevent multiple Defer Alarm dialogs for the same event."
msgstr "Preveni multiple dialogos de Differe Alarmas per le mesme evento."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kalarm.appdata.xml:61
msgid ""
"If Defer is disabled for a notification alarm, don't show two Edit buttons."
msgstr ""
"Si Defere es dishabilitate per un alarma de notification,non monstra duo "
"buttones de Editar."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kalarm.appdata.xml:69
msgid ""
"If a recurrence is suppressed by work time/holidays/exception, suppress its "
"sub-repetitions."
msgstr ""
"Si un recurrentia es supprimite per tempore de labor/ferias/exception, "
"supprime su sub-repetitiones."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kalarm.appdata.xml:70
msgid ""
"Improvements and bug fixes to recurrence/work time/holidays calculations."
msgstr ""
"Melioramentos e correctiones de faltas per calculationes de recurrentia/"
"tempore da labor/ ferias."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kalarm.appdata.xml:71
msgid "Fix formatting of user messages which showed HTML tags."
msgstr ""
"Corrige fnormatar de messages de usator que monstrava etiquettas (tags) HTML."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kalarm.appdata.xml:72
msgid ""
"Distinguish between daily and minutely sub-repetitions in alarm calendar."
msgstr ""
"Distingue inter sub-repetitiones quotidian e de minutas in calendario de "
"alarmas."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kalarm.appdata.xml:73
msgid ""
"Only mark calendars as 'KeepFormat' if the user declines to update them."
msgstr ""
"Marca solmente como 'ManteneFormato' si le usator refusa actualisar los."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kalarm.appdata.xml:82
msgid ""
"If an alarm is late-cancelled, don't remove the event if a sub-repetition is "
"still due."
msgstr ""
"Si un alarma es cancellate-en-retardo, non remove le evento si un sub "
"repetition es ancora debite."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kalarm.appdata.xml:83
msgid ""
"Fix infinite loop when alarms trigger, if they are read-only or if the "
"calendar is non-writable."
msgstr ""
"Corrige le loop infinite quando un alarma discatena,si illos es de sol "
"lectura o si le calendario non es scribibile."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kalarm.appdata.xml:84
msgid ""
"In edit dialog, don't display high accuracy warning if start time is before "
"now."
msgstr ""
"In dialogo de editar, non monstra aviso de alte precision si le tempore  de "
"initio es ante nunc."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kalarm.appdata.xml:93
msgid "Remove excess spacing in Preferences dialog."
msgstr "Remove spatiar de excesso in dialogo de Preferentias."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kalarm.appdata.xml:101
msgid "Prevent message windows taking keyboard focus when they pop up."
msgstr ""
"Preveni que le fenestras de message prende le foco de claviero quando illos "
"emerge como popup."

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.kalarm.appdata.xml:111
msgid "Implement audio backends as plugins to allow user selection."
msgstr ""
"Implementa retro administrationes audio como plugins per permitter selection "
